  "text": "We end this section with the fact that taking pointwise maximum or minimum preserves the property of being represented by a ReLU DNN. One can find similar results in [CITATION_1] Lemma A.3] , where the authors adopt a different notation of neural network by allowing connections between nodes in non-consecutive layers. ",
